data.description: This home will sell itself!  Practically everything has been replaced or updated!  New electrical, windows, siding, furnace and central air, water softener, flooring, remodeled kitchen with custom cabinets, remodeled master bath with two person jacuzzi tub and light fixtures throughout the house.  If you are looking for privacy this home is the last one on a dead end street with a view of the woods.  The 2 1/2 car garage offers a huge workshop area.  All of this and only one block from Pymatuning Lake!
